# Buildroot external tree – BigTreeTech PandaTouch
#
# This file is intentionally minimal: all board-specific configuration
# lives in configs/esp32s3_pandatouch_defconfig and in the board/
# directory, so no extra Kconfig symbols are needed right now.
#
# To add custom packages in the future, add:
#   source "$BR2_EXTERNAL_PANDATOUCH_PATH/package/<name>/Config.in"
